{"thig12.1:0.1":"Therigatha 12.1 ","thig12.1:0.2":"Solasakanipata ","thig12.1:0.3":"Punnatherigatha ","thig12.1:1.1":"“Udahari aham site, ","thig12.1:1.2":"sada udakamotarim; ","thig12.1:1.3":"Ayyanam dandabhayabhita, ","thig12.1:1.4":"vacadosabhayattita. ","thig12.1:2.1":"Kassa brahmana tvam bhito, ","thig12.1:2.2":"sada udakamotari; ","thig12.1:2.3":"Vedhamanehi gattehi, ","thig12.1:2.4":"sitam vedayase bhusam”. ","thig12.1:3.1":"“Jananti vata mam bhoti, ","thig12.1:3.2":"punnike paripucchasi; ","thig12.1:3.3":"Karontam kusalam kammam, ","thig12.1:3.4":"rundhantam katapapakam. ","thig12.1:4.1":"Yo ca vuddho daharo va, ","thig12.1:4.2":"papakammam pakubbati; ","thig12.1:4.3":"Dakabhisecana sopi, ","thig12.1:4.4":"papakamma pamuccati”. ","thig12.1:5.1":"“Ko nu te idamakkhasi, ","thig12.1:5.2":"ajanantassa ajanako; ","thig12.1:5.3":"Dakabhisecana nama, ","thig12.1:5.4":"papakamma pamuccati. ","thig12.1:6.1":"Saggam nuna gamissanti, ","thig12.1:6.2":"sabbe mandukakacchapa; ","thig12.1:6.3":"Naga ca susumara ca, ","thig12.1:6.4":"ye canne udake cara. ","thig12.1:7.1":"Orabbhika sukarika, ","thig12.1:7.2":"macchika migabandhaka; ","thig12.1:7.3":"Cora ca vajjhaghata ca, ","thig12.1:7.4":"ye canne papakammino; ","thig12.1:7.5":"Dakabhisecana tepi, ","thig12.1:7.6":"papakamma pamuccare. ","thig12.1:8.1":"Sace ima nadiyo te, ","thig12.1:8.2":"papam pubbe katam vahum; ","thig12.1:8.3":"Punnampima vaheyyum te, ","thig12.1:8.4":"tena tvam paribahiro. ","thig12.1:9.1":"Yassa brahmana tvam bhito, ","thig12.1:9.2":"sada udakamotari; ","thig12.1:9.3":"Tameva brahme ma kasi, ","thig12.1:9.4":"ma te sitam chavim hane”. ","thig12.1:10.1":"“Kummaggapatipannam mam, ","thig12.1:10.2":"ariyamaggam samanayi; ","thig12.1:10.3":"Dakabhisecana bhoti, ","thig12.1:10.4":"imam satam dadami te”. ","thig12.1:11.1":"“Tuyheva satako hotu, ","thig12.1:11.2":"nahamicchami satakam; ","thig12.1:11.3":"Sace bhayasi dukkhassa, ","thig12.1:11.4":"sace te dukkhamappiyam. ","thig12.1:12.1":"Makasi papakam kammam, ","thig12.1:12.2":"avi va yadi va raho; ","thig12.1:12.3":"Sace ca papakam kammam, ","thig12.1:12.4":"karissasi karosi va. ","thig12.1:13.1":"Na te dukkha pamutyatthi, ","thig12.1:13.2":"upeccapi palayato; ","thig12.1:13.3":"Sace bhayasi dukkhassa, ","thig12.1:13.4":"sace te dukkhamappiyam. ","thig12.1:14.1":"Upehi saranam buddham, ","thig12.1:14.2":"dhammam sanghanca tadinam; ","thig12.1:14.3":"Samadiyahi silani, ","thig12.1:14.4":"tam te atthaya hehiti”. ","thig12.1:15.1":"“Upemi saranam buddham, ","thig12.1:15.2":"dhammam sanghanca tadinam; ","thig12.1:15.3":"Samadiyami silani, ","thig12.1:15.4":"tam me atthaya hehiti. ","thig12.1:16.1":"Brahmabandhu pure asim, ","thig12.1:16.2":"ajjamhi saccabrahmano; ","thig12.1:16.3":"Tevijjo vedasampanno, ","thig12.1:16.4":"sottiyo camhi nhatako”ti. ","thig12.1:17.1":"… Punna theri …. ","thig12.1:18.1":"Solasakanipato nitthito. "}